column2: select p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, s.z as redshift, s.zErr as errzspec, s.specobjid from galaxy p, specobj s, galSpecExtra g, dbo.fgetNearByObjEq(#,#, #) n where p.objid=s.bestobjid and p.objid=n.objid and g.SpecObjID=s.SpecObjID and s.bestobjid=n.objid and s.z BETWEEN # AND # AND p.clean=# AND s.zWarning=#
